@startuml TouristaStudio_UC_DangNhap
!theme plain

title UC02 — DANG KY / DANG NHAP TAI KHOAN

' ============================================================
' ACTORS
' ============================================================
actor "Nguoi dung" as USER
actor "He thong Email" as EMAIL

' ============================================================
' SYSTEM BOUNDARY
' ============================================================
rectangle "He thong Tourista Studio" {

    ' --- Use Cases ---
    (Dang ky tai khoan\n(email + password)) as UC01
    (Dang nhap\n(email + password)) as UC02
    (Dang nhap Google) as UC03
    (Dang nhap Facebook) as UC04
    (Xac thuc email\n(ma OTP)) as UC05
    (Quen mat khau\n(va dat lai)) as UC06
    (Dang xuat) as UC07

    ' --- Internal system functions ---
    (Tao JWT Access Token\n(thoi han 15 phut)) as JWT_ACC
    (Tao Refresh Token\n(thoi han 7 ngay)) as JWT_REF
    (Ma hoa mat khau\n(BCrypt)) as BCRYPT
}

' ============================================================
' RELATIONSHIPS
' ============================================================

USER --> UC01
USER --> UC02
USER --> UC03
USER --> UC04
USER --> UC05
USER --> UC06
USER --> UC07

EMAIL --> UC05

' UC includes internal functions
UC01 .down.> BCRYPT : <<include>>
UC01 .down.> UC05 : <<include>>

UC02 .down.> BCRYPT : <<include>>
UC02 .down.> JWT_ACC : <<include>>
UC02 .down.> JWT_REF : <<include>>

UC03 .down.> JWT_ACC : <<include>>
UC03 .down.> JWT_REF : <<include>>

UC04 .down.> JWT_ACC : <<include>>
UC04 .down.> JWT_REF : <<include>>

UC06 .down.> EMAIL : <<include>>

' ============================================================
' NOTES
' ============================================================
note bottom of UC01
  **Luong Dang ky:**
  1. Nhap email, password, ho ten
  2. Ma hoa password (BCrypt)
  3. Luu vao CSDL
  4. Gui email xac thuc
  5. Nhan link xac thuc trong email
end note

note bottom of UC02
  **Luong Dang nhap:**
  1. Nhap email, password
  2. Kiem tra BCrypt hash
  3. Tao JWT Access Token (15 phut)
  4. Tao Refresh Token (7 ngay)
  5. Tra token ve Frontend
end note

note bottom of UC03
  **Luong Google OAuth2:**
  1. Nhan "Dang nhap Google"
  2. Chuyen sang trang Google
  3. Cho phep truy cap
  4. Quay lai + tao JWT
  (Khong can nhap mat khau)
end note

note bottom of UC06
  **Luong Quen mat khau:**
  1. Nhap email da dang ky
  2. He thong gui email dat lai
  3. Nhan link trong email
  4. Nhap mat khau moi
  5. Cap nhat vao CSDL
end note

note top of JWT_ACC
  JWT Access Token:
  - Thoi han: 15 phut
  - Dung de goi API
end note

note top of JWT_REF
  Refresh Token:
  - Thoi han: 7 ngay
  - Dung de lay Access Token moi
end note

note top of BCRYPT
  BCrypt Password:
  - Thuong toan hash mat khau
  - Khong the dao nguoc
end note

@enduml
